nodes.text: Star Wars Search and Find Volume II

Star Wars Search and Find Volume II is a search and find book including scenes from Star Wars: Episode VII The Force Awakens and Star Wars: Episode VIII The Last Jedi. It was released on May 28, 2019.
Travel to a galaxy far, far away in Star Wars Search and Find Vol. II!

Travel across the Star Wars galaxy and explore sixteen illustrated scenes from The Force Awakens and The Last Jedi in this fun, search-and-find collection! Rey, Finn, and Chewbacca are counting on you to stay ahead of Kylo Ren! Think you've defeated the First Order? Hit the hyperdrive and blast to the back of the book for even more search-and-find adventures!
